    "description": "GIMIC Co., Ltd. develops and operates a medical service software. It offers Doctor's File, a medical information site; Hospitals File, a hospital-based medical information site, as well as medical information magazine and veterinary clinic information site; Doctor's File Medipathy, an information sharing app for medical institutions; Doctor's File Apo Registus, a reservation management system that supports the management of medical institutions; Doctor's File Apo, a web reservation management system for clinics; and Doctor's File LINK, a website creation service for clinics. The company also provides Doctor's File Clinico, a clinic-specific personnel evaluation/human resource management system; Doctor's File Jobs, a medical job information site; Doctor's File Agent, a job change support service for medical professionals; and Human Resources Outpatient Center, a personnel consultation service for clinics. In addition, it offers D-Search, a medical collaboration platform; Hospitals that Value Medical Collaboration, an information platform booklet; and MedicallianceDAY, an in-person regional medical cooperation event, as well as Clinic Mirai Lab, a clinic management support media that supports private practice physicians and doctors. GIMIC Co., Ltd. was incorporated in 2003 and is based in Shibuya, Japan."
